<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Error - Page Not Found - Stayzio</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #fe424d;
            --dark-color: #333333;
            --light-color: #f4f4f4;
            --font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-family);
            color: var(--dark-color);
            background-color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden; /* Prevent scrollbar from animation */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            opacity: 0; /* Start hidden for fade-in */
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards;
        }

        /* Keyframe for general fade-in */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            line-height: 1;
            animation: bounceIn 1s ease-out forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.5s; /* Delay for effect */
            opacity: 0;
        }

        @keyframes bounceIn {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.3); }
            50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.05); }
            70% { transform: scale(0.9); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
        }

        .error-graphic {
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin: 1.5rem auto 2rem; /* Adjusted margin */
            position: relative;
            animation: wander 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }
        
        @keyframes wander {
            0% { transform: translateX(0px) translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: translateX(5px) translateY(-5px) rotate(2deg); }
            50% { transform: translateX(-5px) translateY(5px) rotate(-2deg); }
            75% { transform: translateX(5px) translateY(0px) rotate(1deg); }
            100% { transform: translateX(0px) translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
        }

        .error-graphic .stroke {
            stroke: var(--dark-color);
        }
        
        .error-graphic .accent {
            fill: var(--primary-color);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        h1 span {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 1rem 0 2.5rem;
            color: #666;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #e43a45;
            transform: translateY(1px); /* Subtle press effect */
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .nav-links {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-links p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
            color: #888;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            display: inline-block; /* Needed for transform */
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--dark-color);
            transform: translateY(-2px); /* Subtle lift */
        }
        
        /* Responsive styles */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .error-code {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .nav-links {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }
            .nav-links a {
                margin: 0;
            }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="error-code">404</div>

        <svg class="error-graphic" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle class="stroke" cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="none" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line class="stroke" x1="50" y1="15" x2="50" y2="30" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line class="stroke" x1="50" y1="70" x2="50" y2="85" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line class="stroke" x1="15" y1="50" x2="30" y2="50" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <line class="stroke" x1="70" y1="50" x2="85" y2="50" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <path class="accent" d="M50 25 L60 50 L50 75 L40 50 Z" />
            <circle class="stroke" cx="50" cy="50" r="5" fill="white" stroke-width="2"/>
            <text x="47" y="55" font-size="12" font-family="Montserrat, sans-serif" font-weight="700" fill="#333">?</text>
        </svg>

        <h1>Oops! <span>Wrong Turn?</span></h1>

        <p>
            The page you're searching for seems to have embarked on its own adventure and gone off the map. Let's guide you back to familiar territory!
        </p>

        <a href="/" class="cta-button">Back to Homepage</a>

        <div class="nav-links">
            <p>Or navigate to one of these popular routes:</p>
            <div>
                <a href="/listings">Explore Destinations</a>
                <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
<script>
  // Check on page load
  if (!navigator.onLine) {
    window.location.href = '/offline';
  }

  // Listen for going offline while browsing
  window.addEventListener('offline', () => {
    window.location.href = '/offline';
  });
</script>


</body>
</html>